Monster Rewards
Monster Rewards is an innovative iOS banking application that merges traditional financial management with engaging gaming elements. It transforms personal finance management into an enjoyable and educational experience, encouraging users to interact with their financial accounts through a unique gaming experience.

Description
Monster Rewards offers a novel approach to personal banking by integrating typical banking functionalities, such as checking account balances and transferring funds, with a gamified system of experience points (XP) and levels. Users earn rewards and level up as they engage in financial activities, making the mundane task of managing finances more interactive and fun.

Features
Account Management: View checking and savings account balances.
Transfers: Utilize features like Zelle for money transfers.
Gaming Integration: Earn XP points and level up by participating in financial activities.
Rewards System: Accumulate rewards like Capital One miles, Walmart credits, Amazon credits, and Target credits.
Interactive UI: Enjoy a user interface that transforms banking into a game.
Getting Started
Dependencies
Designed specifically for iOS, developed using SwiftUI.
Backend services simulated in Node.js (Note: This app does not integrate real banking APIs).
Installing and Running
Clone the repository:
bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/pc9350/Banking_App.git
Open the project in Xcode.
Run the app using the iOS simulator.
Usage
Upon launching Monster Rewards:

Log in with the provided mock credentials.
Explore and interact with various banking features.
Perform activities to earn XP and level up.
Keep track of and redeem your accumulated rewards.

